May White https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/May_White 0 May White (1889 - 18 October 1979) was an American silent film actress. May White worked as an actress with Essanay Studios in Niles, California, before leaving with Charlie Chaplin for Los Angeles. May_White ( 1889 - 18_October_1979 ) was an_American_silent_film_actress . May_White worked as an_actress with Essanay_Studios in Niles , California , before leaving with Charlie_Chaplin for Los_Angeles .
